r relationship between when content was released and when it was added to Netflix.\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"JdVFZ7YDs39i"}},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":607},"id":"05ce5673","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1775594826809,"user_tz":-120,"elapsed":311,"user":{"displayName":"Ahmed Abdullah","userId":"01226176949767729422"}},"outputId":"14e98f4c-1b07-40ef-94cf-fe8efb81140d"},"source":["plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n","sns.scatterplot(x='release_year', y='year_added', data=NF, alpha=0.6)\n","plt.title('Scatter Plot of Release Year vs. Year Added on Netflix')\n","plt.xlabel('Release Year')\n","plt.ylabel('Year Added to Netflix')\n","plt.grid(True, linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)\n","plt.tight_layout()\n","plt.show()"],"execution_count":41,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1000x600 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["I will identify the top 5 years with the most releases by counting the occurrences of each release year and then selecting the top 5."],"metadata":{"id":"0GUWlgCvtfcJ"}},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"2932aba9","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1775594898267,"user_tz":-120,"elapsed":7,"user":{"displayName":"Ahmed Abdullah","userId":"01226176949767729422"}},"outputId":"34ed710b-fe1d-4934-822e-3904d61e519b"},"source":["top_5_release_years = NF['release_year'].value_counts().head(5)\n","print(\"Top 5 years with the most releases:\")\n","print(top_5_release_years)"],"execution_count":42,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Top 5 years with the most releases:\n","release_year\n","2019    613\n","2018    600\n","2020    581\n","2017    446\n","2021    385\n","Name: count, dtype: int64\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"bb9e34ea","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1775595184127,"user_tz":-120,"elapsed":7,"user":{"displayName":"Ahmed Abdullah","userId":"01226176949767729422"}},"outputId":"078c1b14-d2e8-442b-a6b3-42f008fda0cb"},"source":["# Identify the year with the least number of releases\n","least_releases_year = NF['release_year'].value_counts().idxmin()\n","least_releases_count = NF['release_year'].value_counts().min()\n","print(f\"The year with the least number of releases is {least_releases_year} with {least_releases_count} release(s).\")"],"execution_count":48,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["The year with the least number of releases is 1961 with 1 release(s).\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"8385ab7b"},"source":["**Summary of Cleaning Steps and Generated Insights**\n","\n","**Data Cleaning Steps:**\n","\n","1.  **Missing Data:**\n","    *   Identified missing values in the `type` column and replaced them with 'Unknown'.\n","\n","2.  **Messy Data:**\n","    *   Removed `**` from the `title` column.\n","    *   Converted the date format of the `date_added` column from \"M/D/YYYY\" to \"M-D-YYYY\".\n","    *   Cleaned the `release_year` column by removing various bad characters (`(`, `)`, `c`, `C`, `.`, ` `, `S`, `s`) and converted it to a numeric type, coercing errors to `NaN` (though no `NaN`s resulted from this cleaning).\n","    *   Cleaned the `rating` column by removing `,?` and replacing mid-hyphens with underscores.\n","\n","3.  **Relevant Data:**\n","    *   Split the `listed_in` column by commas and kept only the first category for each entry.\n","\n","**Generated Insights:**\n","\n","1.  **Content Type Prominence:**\n","    *   Netflix predominantly features **Movies (87.8%)** over **TV Shows (12.2%)**.\n","\n","2.  **Year with Least Releases:**\n","    *   The year with the least number of releases is **1961** with **1** release(s).\n","\n","3.  **Distinct Ratings:**\n","    *   The Netflix dataset contains **11 distinct ratings**, with 'TV_MA' and 'TV_14' being the most frequent.\n","\n","4.  **Category Frequency:**\n","    *   'Stand-Up Comedy' is the most common category (6.22%), followed by 'Dramas, International Movies' (5.60%), and 'Comedies, Dramas, International Movies' (5.22%).\n","\n","5.  **Historical Trend of Release Year:**\n","    *   The distribution of content release years shows trends in content additions over time. The top 5 years with the most releases are 2019, 2018, 2020, 2017, and 2021.\n","\n","6.  **Correlation between 'release_year' and 'year_added':**\n","    *   A very weak positive linear correlation (approximately 0.0175) was found between the release year of content and when it was added to Netflix, indicating almost no direct relationship."]}]}